        <content><![CDATA[<p>By clicking on the on the <strong>Clipboard</strong> icon&nbsp;<img style="width: 14px;" title="clipboardBigIconActive" src="%(link0)" alt="" /> in the toolbar you can access your personal favorites and a list of elements you have recently used. You can directly add content from the clipboard to your page by drag &amp; drop.</p>]]></content>
